<args_desc>
- `-python`: Activates Python mode. Creates launch files for `uv` and `pip`.
</args_desc>
<md>
#### Python Mode (`-python`)
Activates Python mode. Creates launch files:
*   `setup_run(uv)`: Uses `uv` for fast setup.
*   `run(pip)`: Uses standard `pip`.
</md>